values:
Ok so it's 10:40 on a Wednesday night and I'm sitting at home like I do EVERY NIGHT! Nothing else new right? Yeah, same shit different day. I have no life and it's kinda funny because I spend all my time with or near pops. I live and work with my him, I see him almost 24/7....
 
 We need a bigger place so I can stop sharing a room with him. Yeah that's right we share a room and have been doing so for the past 3 years and counting. But just so you don't think something freaky is going on let me tell you that we have our OWN beds! This is why we need a bigger place to live, but not just any place. I want a place I can call home. Not just another house or apartment. I want to own a house, I want to be able to know that I don't have a landlord. If I want to remodel the basement and make a kick ass gaming room or a movie room out of it I can. God willing, if I ever get a girlfriend I want a place (my room) I can take her that doesn't have pops bed in it as well. I want a room I can call my own where I can have the cord to the X-box hanging in front of the dresser and I don't have to worry about someone coming and unplugging it in the morning because "I couldn't get in to my dresser to get my socks because your cord was in the way". I want to be able to blast KoRn or Slipknot in my room if I want to and not have to think of pops watching TV in the same room or the neighbor down stairs or across the hall. 

Ok I'm done bitching for today, but I'm sure I'll think of something else to bitch and moan about tomorrow or the next day.

Bless me father for it's been many months time since my last confession...

My sister got her permit, God save us all! Hmmm what else...? I got I cell phone, old news but news none the less. Oh and I have 4 more weeks till I leave for Florida for the holidays *does the happy dance* OH YEAH! I'll be there for 2 weeks then I'll be dieing to come home, it gets BORING there after a while. Well other then that my life is just as boring as ever.

Today I heard the greatest news! Ken, The fat bastard that I worked for at Michael's (HELL) quit today! LOL, I'm gone 1 week and that place goes to hell and the fat bastard quits >:). I was also told thay had to hire 5 guys to do the job that I did alone. I think that funny realy. I was talking to Bill on line earler today and said "I leave you in charge and the place goes to Hell! The manager up and quits! *HIGH FIVE* Good Going! :)" 

Hmm so what's been going on? Well nothing's different that I can think of for the most part... Oh but I did get a new cell phone, if you want the # leave me a post and I'll think about giving it to you :P.

Well I've not been to hell (Michael's) in almost a week and yes I miss the people there but not the hassles that came with being me there. I sware I had ot have heard my name called every 5 seconds some of the time or people asking or help. And it seemed as if I were the only one who knew anything about the store and it's products. So that part I don't miss all that much. Well I'm doing the maintenance thing for now and well see how money flows in from that alone. I should be more then fine with it though, seeing as I have nothing or no one to spend it on... but it's all good. What that they say? All good things come in time. Speaking of which, I just got a cell phone of my own. If you want the number just leave a message and I'll see if I want to give it to you :P.

Well lets see what has been going on? Last night was Erin and my going away "party". We had all of 9 people there total. Can you feel the love? To the people that showed up I thank you grately and you shall be missed. To those who couldn't make it, it's been nice knowing you... maybe I'll see you around some time.

It feels strange not having to goto work at Michael's(HELL) anymore. I'm happy but at the same time I'm going to miss going there and seeing the friends I've made over the years. But at the same time I'm happy I never have to go see that fat bastard Ken any more. Or put up with the customers bothering me all the damn time! 

Well... that's pretty much it. Oh and thank you once more to those of you who came last night, and remember we're doing it again in 3 weeks for Mich's party (she's quiting as well).

Well it's been a while sense I've writen anything so here it goes.

These past 2 weeks have been the same as usual, nothing big happening in them and such. I've been getting the screan names of a few of the people I work with that I hadn't had before. That's cool, though I don't see us keeping in contact after I leave for some reason it always works out that way. There is a few people I know will refuse to lose contact with me, they are the stubren ones :P . I was asked last night by John if I was still leaving and I told him yes, so he asked when my last day was and I told him I though it was Saturday but he only had me down for Thursday(tonight) as my last night so ... I offered to work on Saturday 9-5 and he said ok. I don't think he wants me to go, but for different reasons then the other people don't want to see me go. 
For some reason they(the "bosses") have been putting me and this one girl together at work, don't get me wrong I'm not complaning she's a great girl and beautiful in every way. I just find it odd that they put people with me now that I'm leaving more then they used to. 
Monday night I pissed on of the managers Joe pretty good. Ok, Jeff was closeing manager and he doesn't mind me listening to my CD player while sweeping the floor at night. Joe comes in at about 8:45 right before we closed and by this point I had the headphones on for about 30-40 min. Joe said "Headphones" and pointed to his ears. Ok so it's been a while sence I've made a real post in this thing so here it is.

Lets start with friday. Friday pops and I chilled all day insted of working, I took the doughter of the guy who runs the office out to lunch for helping me with something. And no, there's nothing going on there. But then when pops and I are going to the bank to deposit our checks I get a call from my 14 year old cuz named Alex. Alex: "Yo when you coming to my house? the movie starts at 7:40pm..." Me: "Be there in 10, so hold your horses there spanky!". so after a huge fuck up on my part involving SEPTA we get to where we were going. I go up to the counter and said one for Res. evil, I pay then walk in then the girl turns to me and asks how old I am and if I have ID. I'm like "Wut... what for"? Oh this kid's only 14 and he need someone over 21 to see this movie because it's rated R. So by this point in the night I'm like OH HELL NO! this shit is not happening to me now... because of course I have no ID on me on this night. so we get tickets to Paveratizy or how ever the peace of shit movie is spelled. we get out drinks and head up to the girl taking the tickets and I see that the movie is at the same entrance as the one we have tickets for. so I think to myself, why the hell not.. they never check tickets... and you guessed it... 5 min. into the movie a guy with a flashlight comes up to us and says "can I see your tickets" I'm like FUCK! why couldn't Alex just have kept his mouth shut when I started heading for the "wrong" movie and why were the only 2 fucking seats in the damn theater right next to the door. so we get kicked out of that movie and sent to the one we had tickets for *mutter* can I just say it was almost as bad as the spice girls movie...

Then there was yesterday. It was a better day over all, I opened so I was up at 7:00am and in by about 8:45am which gave me time to eat something before clocking in. before going to work I always goto Wawa and get a drink for the day and something for breakfast and lunch. when I got up to the girl my total was $6.66 , she pointed it out and snickered. I said "Hay my lucky number! This is going to be a good day" then I gave an evil grin and went to work. work took forever like old people in a 10 mile foot race. Then came 5:00pm, I clocked out and went with Mish and them to her house for brians suprise BBQ party. let me just say now that a lot of the night is a blur, Brian and I got shit faced and took over the bathroom. He got the tub and I got the toilet, and there we stayed for about and hour or more. we were telling people that needed to use the bathroom that we were not moving and to use the tub. One of the girls snuck in while I left the bathroom and pissed with brian in there after tossing a towel over his head, then she started yelling "I have purple undies!" then from what I hear she showed a few people to prove it. once she left the bathroom I waqs right back in there with my head in the toilet once more, and throwing up the water I was just given becaue I was as white as a ghost. as I lay there Mish tells me she's going to be right back because she's going to get me a bowl so I can go lie down on a bed. Well I get sick and tired of waiting and I fall asleep with my head in the toilet, waking up a while later to her saying "where the hell did they go? no one is watching you 2..." I said "what happened to my bowl?" she's like Oh yeah and she runs down to get one for me, but in the time it takes her to do so I'm in bed and passed out.

And that brings us into this morning. I wake up frezing my ass off. YOU THINK THOSE ASS' WOULD PUT A BLANKET ON THE DRUNK PASSED OUT GUY? NO! *mutter* :P but anyhoo. I find a blanket and look at the clock it's now 5:30 something in the morning... and to top it off I have a spliting headack, cotten mouth, and my eyes are killing me from throwing up so much. after a lot of just trying to wake up and getting a shower I get down stairs to see Erin asleep, brial and chrissy watching a movie. I get something to eat real quick and then get some asprin for the lingering headack. when I was coming back from tossing out my trash from breakfast I saw erin still sleeping so I decided to mess with her and poke her in the top of her head a few times... I got no responce in any way shape or form. so brian and I had a good laugh about it and started watching Ind. Jones, it got to a part that had this chick drink shots and we almost tossed our cookies again... then we got erin up finally and she got a shower and we went to work..yes work...*sobs*

Can I just say sorry to all of you who have ever worked even with a slight hangover... I feel your pain. I felt and liiked like death all day, it was horible. and on top of it everyone wanted to mess with me about it and this didn't help my headack in the least. Buy I would have done this day over again if only not to have to spnd friday night with my cuz, now that was pain... Now I'm home and I feel like a little better but I still can feel the affects of last night and I need sleep and water. 

so that was my weekend in all it's glory. I know there's more but I just don't feel like typing any more so any of you who were there feel free to fill in the blank spots of my night. Oh and note to self: never let brian mix you a drink after he's drunk, they are WAY to strong!

Everything fades as I was lost in you gaze

Never wanting to let you loose

You come near

Once again
Wanting to do so much
But doing so little...
